# Space Shooter (Unity + C#)

A 2D arcade-style space shooter with wave-based enemy spawning and boss mechanics.

---

## Gameplay Overview

Player controls a spaceship, fights enemy waves, and survives increasingly difficult levels.

---

## Features

- Player movement and shooting system
- Wave-based enemy spawning system
- Enemy AI (movement patterns + attack logic)
- Boss fight mechanics
- Score system
- UI system (health, score, game over)

---

## Technical Highlights

- State-based enemy behavior system
- Coroutine-based wave spawning
- Object pooling (if you have it)
- Modular game architecture (GameManager driven)
- Real-time gameplay system design

